cs.RO, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.SY, cs.MA 

The paper focuses on robotics challenges involving micro aerial vehicles (MAVs), which suggests that it belongs to the Robotics (cs.RO) sub-category. The challenges require reliable target perception and mission planning, which involves computer vision (cs.CV) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The coordination of a team of MAVs also involves systems and control (cs.SY) and multi-agent systems (cs.MA).
